children.label: notifyUsage
description: Notify of a registered feature usage at given time.
signature: (featureName: string, usedAt?: number | Date | undefined) => void

children.label: featureName
description: - the name of the feature to notify usage of

children.label: usedAt
description: - Either a `Date` or an unix timestamp with ms. If not specified, it will be set to the current time.

children.label: getLastUsages
description:
Return a map containing last usage timestamp for all features.
Features that were not used yet do not appear in the map.
